result.notes:
Multi-beam echo sounder (MBES) backscatter data collected as part of the 
Darwin Plus funded project " Mapping Anguilla's 'Blue Belt' Ecosystem 
Services". The project aimed to develop local capacity to undertake 
comprehensive marine resource assessments of Anguilla’s ‘Blue-Belt’, 
delivering best practice guidance for combining satellite and acoustic 
surveys, to extend mapping into deeper waters for the first time.
